	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />nmi_on_timing tests NMI timing near the end of vblank by writing with bit 7 ($80) set to $2000. if 5=N, it means your edge timing is 1 PPU cycle off.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


