		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">; Correct output:<br />; 01 N<br />; 02 N<br />; 03 N<br />; 04 N<br />; 05 -<br />; 06 -<br />; 07 -<br />; 08 -<br />; 09 -</div>The numbers don't mean anything <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /> it's just an ordered list. Each next in the list is the result timed at 1 PPU cycle after the previous one.

		

